Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
delete_pg_keepout(25.10)                              delete_pg_keepout(25.10)

Name
       delete_pg_keepout

Syntax
        delete_pg_keepout

       [-help]

       {-cell <lib_cell_name> | -inst <instance_name >| -all }

       [-layer <layer_name> | -layerId <layer_id>]

       Deletes PG keep out boxes in design for user defined objects.

Parameters
       -all   Removes all PG keepout boxes in design.

       -cell <lib_cell_name>
              Specifies  the  lib cell to remove the PG keepout box applied to
              the specified cell.

       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes type and  default  in-
              formation for each delete_pg_keepout parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man delete_pg_keepout

       -inst <instance_name>
              Specifies  the  instance to remove the PG keepout box applied to
              the specified instance.

       -layer <layer_name>
              Specifies the names of the layers to delete the PG  keepout  box
              applied on the specified metal layers.

       -layerId <layer_id>
              Specifies  the layer IDs to delete the PG keepout box applied on
              the specified metal layer.

Related Information
              * report_pg_keepout

              * specify_pg_keepout

